{
  "texts": [
    "As AI matures with more trained algorithms, its applications in epidemiology, host-pathogen interactions, and drug design expand [9].",
    "AI is now used in drug discovery, customized medicine, gene editing, radiography, image processing, and medication management.",
    "AI-based technologies will enable more precise diagnosis and cost-effective treatment in the near future.",
    "In agriculture, AI-based approaches have reduced waste, increased output, and time to market.",
    "Machine learning and deep-learning-based smart programs can modify metabolic pathways of living systems to achieve optimal outputs with minimal inputs."
  ]
}